title: Wordpress loading multiple jQuery Versions
message:
I developed a plugin that uses the jquery booklet plugin (http://builtbywill.com/booklet/#/). This plugin binds a function to $ so I can call $('.myBook').booklet();

I could easily manage the loading order with wp_enqueue_script, so first I load jquery, then I load booklet, so everything is fine.

BUT in my theme I also use jquery via webpack, so the loading order is now the following:

jquery
booklet
app.js (bundled file with webpack, including jquery)
